channel.title: Plz help
channel.description:
ok ive got jdk 6 u 11 jee or something like that and i downloaded allstar scape v2 and then for some reason it says when i try to compile my server it says u do not have a version of jdk 5.0 or 6.0
and then the second thing is
how do i change npc's positions cuz i open up the files like autospawn.cfg and it says what would u like to open this up with and idk what to do from their
but then when i try like doing autospawn.cfg it wont let me backspace to delete one or something it makes like a click sound when i try? can anyone please help me
in regards, derek :cool:

item.title: Plz help
item.dc:creator: @derekc12 derekc12
item.description:
@derekc12 wrote:

[quote=“Dvs Chick, post:2, topic:255793”]Okay well idk about your second problem but I know your first.
Your compiler isn’t set for your type of JDK.

Go to your compiler < edit

Now search in the code where it says jdk1.6_XX

The XX’s are where the numbers should be.
Now backspace those 2 numbers and put in 11.
Save and exit and try it again :)[/quote]
i did that and when i click comile server it says no version of jdk1.6 detected?? any help
